item.title: The Best of my Decade
item.description: In this article, I reflect on some of the best things and moments that I had in the decade 2010-2019. It’s been a wonderful 10 years full of ups and downs and in as much as I would like to have a balanced view of both, I choose to stick with the positive things that happened to me and that I can remember.
